vnPVHg">Sơn thôn tức sự - 山村即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/T%C3%A0n-ty-kh%C3%BAc/poem-ZmNtUgYz08ahaR7WvBi2RQ">Tàn ty khúc - 殘絲曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/author-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Lý Hạ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%87-l%C6%B0-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Nghi%C3%AAm-c%C3%B4ng/poem-ajaEISz5lfE_clXnjE-Bxw">Tệ lư khiển hứng, phụng ký Nghiêm công - 敝廬遣興，奉寄嚴公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Thu%E1%BB%B7-v%C3%A2n-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-369c3zC7phY1UZZy2F9WYg">Thuỷ vân hương - 水雲鄉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br></div>	</div>
